{{short description|Italian film festival}} {{Infobox Film Festival | name = Trieste Film Festival | image = | caption = | location = [[Trieste]], Italy | awards = | founded = 1989 | number = | director = | website = {{url|http://www.triestefilmfestival.it}} }}
The '''Trieste Film Festival''' is an international [[film festival]] founded in 1989.<ref name="Gore2004">{{cite book|author=Chris Gore|title=The ultimate film festival survival guide|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aCPuAAAAMAAJ|date=1 September 2004|publisher=Lone Eagle Pub.|isbn=978-1-58065-057-1}}</ref> Held annually on the third week of January in [[Trieste]], it has become the leading festival of Central and Eastern Europe cinema in Italy.<ref name="Smith2008">{{cite book|author=Ian Haydn Smith|title=International Film Guide|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qUMNAQAAMAAJ|year=2008|publisher=Wallflower Press|isbn=978-1-905674-61-9|page=420}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=The Independent: A Magazine for Video and Filmmakers|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=RuFUAAAAMAAJ|year=2005|publisher=Foundation for Independent Video and Film}}</ref>
